! scope="row" | 3rd p. sg.
| ''han/hun<br />/den/det'' <br /> he/she/it|| ''ham/hende<br />/den/det''<br /> him/her/it|| ''hans/hendes<br />/dens/dets''<br /> his/her/its||  ''hans/hendes<br />/dens/dets''<br /> his/hers/its
